{"tid":1255831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果光環、民意有用？！","createTime":"2019-06-24T16:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T16:32:43.000Z","uid":78709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3da8c81ed8bb20d99ba53916c3a2c5543a44a86e","tid":1255831,"uid":78709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:25:43.000Z","msg":"正所謂得民心得天下！<br />\n<br />\n聽講 只要我地做高質素 和平理性的示威者<br />\n香港人的民心就會向住我地尼邊～<br />\n<br />\n如果尼個立論成立<br />\n咁尼場運動應該越黎越多人支持同參加。<br />\n可以用主流民意壓倒政府！<br />\n但點解而家越黎越少人？越黎越無noise?<br />\n而且主流民意想要民主好耐啦。<br />\n點解政府都係無回應？越黎越赤化？<br />\n<br />\n爭取民意絕對沒錯<br />\n但請不要再被民意/光環限制對抗爭的想象力。"},{"pid":"a43f6ef06726dbeb5b75aae1793b080903760718","tid":1255831,"uid":193072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"因為主流意見唔係民主社會<br />\n<br />\n你見一班廢老幾愛國就知咩事啦"},{"pid":"5bb8b708d1bd12a81da34f667d27a57817e13670","tid":1255831,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a43f6ef06726dbeb5b75aae1793b080903760718","tid":1255831,"uid":193072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:28:54.000Z","msg":"因為主流意見唔係民主社會<br />\n<br />\n你見一班廢老幾愛國就知咩事啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8fFf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8fFf9.jpg&h=c6019c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKRASFu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKRASFu.png&h=eac30445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【警民大和解】警方高層不代表前線 市民應支持前線警員!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251511\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67df6c23bf8985cb271f88f62d11757de339c1b5","tid":1255831,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"為左626！落地做宣傳！